name: The Flow
description:
Here and now, is undead.

Every past was once a now, every future will be a now. There in one’s mind is here in others. Here and now is a dynamic and versatile concept.

The only thing that stay, is change. Constantly changing and moving it will not stop easy. 

Flow like water all texts, tunes, tones, textures adapts together strong

HicetNunc is not dead
#HENUNDEAD

Analog collage made from paper waste on canvas board
16 November 2021 |  @elsadiora
